parameters:
\nc<Employee>Meary-senpai, it seems like they're having a serious
conversation... Should we eavesdrop?

\nc<Senpai>So, you're saying it's Saki's fault that one of your
employees caught a cold and had to take time off, and you
want compensation for that, right?

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>I don't know anything about those guys. (Surely, they're not
really going to ask for compensation, right?)

\nc<Senpai>Instead, let's agree that there will be no more dispatches
from our team from now on...
\nc<Senpai>Oh? Have you changed your mind already?

\bustMsgExp[2, 2]\nc<Senpai>That's what I thought. I knew you were calling dispatches
from our team just before your employees' sexual desires
were about to explode.
\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Yes, then please continue to count on us.

\nc<Senpai>Saki, good work. You can take it easy with your schedule
today.

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Ah, you were watching. Thank you...\bustMsgExp[1, 1] Wait,
you knew and still sent me on dispatch?

\nc<Senpai>I believed that you could handle it, Saki. Let's do our best
today as well♥
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>If that's the case, please don't believe in me...
